== About me
I am an incoming 4th year undergraduate student from Xi'an Jiaotong-Liverpool University, majoring in Information and Computing Science, Department of Intelligent Science, School of Advanced Technology.\n
- Major: Information and Computing Science(It is a confusing major name because what we learn is actually Computer Science)
- Rank: Year 1: 1 \/ 173, Year 2: 1 \/ 430, Year 3: 5 \/ 290 (formal number of total candidates in Year 3 will be released in this September)
- Overall GPA: 3.99 / 4.0
- Major GPA: 4.0 / 4.0

